Itulah kali pertama saya melihat awak.

333
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:23,740
Anda bersinar dengan cemerlang.

334
00:28:25,230 --> 00:28:26,070
Simu,

335
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,230
